{
  "stem": "15732.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There we started to organize, for instance-- as an example one took all the orphans, young children, not so young children, and they were all organized-- we called them kibbutzim, because it was the form that were organized.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were eating together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were consuming together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One had, for instance, the washing to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other had cleaning and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So therefore, they were called kibbutzim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was-- usually there was a leader of the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the aim was always to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The whole organization was the aim was only to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At that time, everybody that survived concentration camp or Germans in any form, they all wanted to have-- to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Later, when it took years to stay in the displacement camps and there was no way out of going to Palestine, because the English refused to give the certificate, then people started going to America and to Australia and to any other place far away from Europe, only to escape Europe and never to see Europe again.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I tried to help wherever I could, with the little bit-- little bit of schooling that I had, I-- I taught the children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I taught them about geography, about continents, about the sun, about the-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not an organized like a school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We called it spreche, talks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked with the children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they usually asked me things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted-- what are you interested to know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I know the answer, then I give the answer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or about history something, about Jewish history a little bit, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they all were studying Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried the little bit that everybody knew, he-- he shared it with-- with the others.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
